videos.headline: Louisville strikes first with 17-yard TD run
videos.description: Louisville's Jawon Pass weaves through the defense for a 17-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Francois gets Florida State on the board with 17-yard TD
videos.description: Deondre Francois connects with Nyqwan Murray for a 17-yard Florida State touchdown.

videos.headline: Pass finds Crum for 4-yard Louisville TD
videos.description: Louisville's Jawon Pass throws to Micky Crum in the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisville's Pass completes 3-yard TD to Fitzpatrick
videos.description: Jawon Pass throws to Dez Fitzpatrick for a 3-yard Louisville touchdown.

videos.headline: Francois finds Terry for 55-yard Florida State TD
videos.description: Deondre Francois goes deep to Tamorrion Terry for a 55-yard Florida State touchdown.

videos.headline: Francois connects with McNitty for 3rd TD pass of game
videos.description: Florida State's Deondre Francois passes to Tre' McNitty for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Samuels III makes game-winning INT for FSU
videos.description: Florida State's Stanford Samuels III intercepts a throw by Jawon Pass to seal the 28-24 victory for the Seminoles.
